<concept id="splinesegs" xml:lang="en-US">
   <title id="title__Toc50995649">SPLINESEGS System Variable</title>
   <conbody>
      <section><title>Spline segments</title><p>Specifies how many line segments are to be generated for each spline-fit polyline (spline option of the PEDIT command). Values between -32768 and 32768 are accepted. With a negative value a fit-type curve is applied. A fit-type curve is composed of arc-segments, which yields a smoother curve, but it takes longer to generate.</p><p><table id="table_r32_ncz_hnb">
               <tgroup cols="2">
                  <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1*" />
                  <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="3*" />
                  <tbody>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/type" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/short" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/saved_in" />
                        <entry><p conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/drawing" /></entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/range" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>32768 to 32767</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                     <row>
                        <entry conkeyref="system_variable_warehouse/default_value" />
                        <entry>
                           <p>8</p>
                        </entry>
                     </row>
                  </tbody>
               </tgroup>
            </table></p></section>
   </conbody>
</concept>
